OL,7,FSpeaking publicly for the first time
OL,8,FTanya Addison shares the abuse she
OL,9,Fexperienced whilst working for former
OL,10,Fowner of Harrods, Mohamed Al Fayed,
OL,11,FITV News Correspondent Sejal Karia
OL,12,Freports.
OL,14,FSome readers may find details of this
OL,15,Freport distressing.
OL,17,FFor more than two decades Mohamed Al
OL,18,FFayed used the glamour and prestige of
OL,19,FHarrods to seek out and prey on dozens
OL,20,Fof young women.
