OL,7,FWomen who claim they were subjected to
OL,8,Fhorrific sexual abuse.
OL,10,F"I was on a sofa in the office, and he
OL,11,Fwas on top of me," Tanya Addison
OL,12,Frecalled. "I knew I needed to get him
OL,13,Foff and there was a struggle. He was
OL,14,Fassaulting me. He was attacking me."
OL,16,FMs Addison was 23 years old when she
OL,17,Fbegan working for him as a personal
OL,18,Fassistant. She said the abuse began
OL,19,Falmost immediately and ended several
OL,20,Fmonths later with Al Fayed trying to
OL,21,Frape her.
