OL,7,F"I was very frightened. I didn't even
OL,8,Fring and tell my parents. I just felt
OL,9,Fhumiliated and ashamed...really deeply
OL,10,Fashamed," she said.
OL,12,FThis is the first time she has spoken
OL,13,Fpublicly about the abuse and she told
OL,14,FITV News that the office was far from
OL,15,Fa safe space and a place she dreaded
OL,16,Fgoing to everyday.
OL,18,FMs Addison claims she was "molested"
OL,19,Fevery time Al Fayed called her into
OL,20,Fhis office one-to-one.
