OL,7,F"Somebody would come out and say 'Mr.
OL,8,FFayed would like you to go in to see
OL,9,Fhim'," she added.
OL,11,FOnce inside "he would pull you down,
OL,12,Fmake you sit on his lap, and he would
OL,13,Fsort of kiss you on the mouth. He
OL,14,Fwould bring out wads of money, pull
OL,15,Fopen your top and shove it down into
OL,16,Fyour bra."
OL,18,F"How many times were you called in?"
OL,19,FITV News Correspondent Sejal Karia
OL,20,Fasked Ms Addison.
