OL,7,F"It was regular. It was every week."
OL,9,FShe said she succumbed out of fear of
OL,10,Fa man with power and influence who
OL,11,Fpresided over a toxic culture of
OL,12,Fsecrecy, intimidation, and the fear of
OL,13,Frepercussions.
OL,15,F"The network of people that he had
OL,16,Faround him to protect him was a
OL,17,Fterrifying environment. It's not easy
OL,18,Fto explain that to someone unless
OL,19,Fyou've been in it," she said.
