OL,7,FEven getting the job had been
OL,8,Fconditional on an intrusive medical
OL,9,Fcheck in Harley Street, London, Ms
OL,10,FAddison recalled.
OL,12,F"I was seeing his (Al Fayed's)
OL,13,Fpersonal physician who was called Dr
OL,14,FAnn Coxon. She did a normal medical
OL,15,Fbut she also did a pelvic exam and
OL,16,Ftook some swab.
OL,18,F"She then told me that I had to have
OL,19,Fan HIV test. She said that I could
OL,20,Frefuse but unfortunately I wouldn't be
OL,21,Fable to take up the position."
