OL,7,FHarrods is now encouraging survivors
OL,8,Fto come forward and apply to the
OL,9,Fcompany's own abuse compensation
OL,10,Fscheme without having to resort to
OL,11,Fformal court proceedings.
OL,13,FWhen asked about how she found dealing
OL,14,Fdirectly with Harrods'
OL,15,Frepresentatives, Ms Addison called the
OL,16,Fprocess "frustrating".
OL,18,F"It feels to me that they really don't
OL,19,Fknow what they're doing, that they are
OL,20,Fliterally making this up as they're
OL,21,Fgoing along.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
