OL,7,F"A process which is so bewildering,
OL,8,Fone that I don't understand, that
OL,9,Fchanges almost on a daily basis," and
OL,10,F"a compensation scheme which just
OL,11,Fseems absolutely fraught with missed
OL,12,Fpromises and poor communication."
OL,14,FHarrods has said previously it had
OL,15,Falready settled a number of claims for
OL,16,Fcompensation.
OL,18,FMs Addison said she's now been told
OL,19,Fthe process has been delayed until at
OL,20,Fleast April.
