OL,7,FIn a statement it said: "Harrods has,
OL,8,Fsince the beginning of this process,
OL,9,Fcommitted to developing a scheme
OL,10,Fquickly to settle and support
OL,11,Fsurvivors, whilst ensuring that the
OL,12,Fscheme is as robust, fair and
OL,13,Ftransparent for survivors as possible.
OL,14,Fbased on feedback from our independent
OL,15,Fadvisors, it has become clear that a
OL,16,Fperiod of consultation is important,
OL,17,Fduring which we are receiving feedback
OL,18,Ffrom all parties, including legal
OL,19,Ffirms representing survivors, leading
OL,20,Fcounsel, and survivors.
