OL,7,F"While it was initially anticipated
OL,8,Fthat application forms would be issued
OL,9,Fbefore Christmas, it has become clear
OL,10,Fthat longer is needed to allow this
OL,11,Fconsultation process, with the
OL,12,Fcommitment now made that it will be up
OL,13,Fand running by April."
OL,15,FThe company also has human rights
OL,16,Fcampaigner Dame Jasvinder Sanghera as
OL,17,Fan advocate for the survivors. She was
OL,18,Fpreviously hired by the Church of
OL,19,FEngland to help them confront their
OL,20,Fabuse allegations.
